game.name: Fashion Girl New Dress
game.description:
You are the biggest fashion designer of your city and today you have got a big project to take care of. Yes, three beautiful ladies are waiting for you outside who have to prepare for three different events. Would you think that you are a perfect choice for this job? Join Fashion Girl New Dress game and be prepared to help three gorgeous women to choose three different outfits! Make sure to change your taste on the basis of each event.

These three different occasions will include Walk to the Mall, Walk to the Park and Walk to the School. Start this game by helping the first girl to choose a perfect dress for the mall in this HTML5 dressing game! Give her a nice hairstyle, change her eyes and skin color, and then get ready to dress up her with a short blue shining dress, a long blue gown with some flares at its bottom or a short red frock with a flower print belt! You can also choose a nice top and pair it with a pair of blue jeans, a short red skirt or a long purple skirt.

Complete her look with a matching pair of sandals, a handbag, and jewelry items! Now dress up the second girl for the second event by choosing a comfortable and stylish outfit for the outing in the park. Third girl wants your help to get ready for the school so mix and match as many school outfits until you create a perfect uniform for her. Hey ladies! It looks you have done a great job during your all three projects! Good luck to play more popular tiles from the category of free dressing games and have a blast without download!
